1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,640
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:41,583 --> 00:00:44,416
She outshines all others in training,

4
00:00:44,625 --> 00:00:46,833
making all the male guards lose face.

5
00:00:47,291 --> 00:00:49,708
Now she wants to take my place?

6
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:53,833
How could I allow that?

7
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:55,500
Mr. Lu has arrived.

8
00:00:58,250 --> 00:00:59,750
Greetings, Mr. Lu.

9
00:01:01,416 --> 00:01:03,833
Shen Bingfan, aren't you impressive?

10
00:01:03,833 --> 00:01:04,750
I heard

11
00:01:04,958 --> 00:01:06,125
not one of the male guards here

12
00:01:06,125 --> 00:01:07,166
can beat you.

13
00:01:08,833 --> 00:01:10,291
Do you have the nerve

14
00:01:10,583 --> 00:01:12,541
to spar with me?

15
00:01:12,875 --> 00:01:13,666
Mr. Lu,

16
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:15,666
Bingfan is recovering from her injury.

17
00:01:16,791 --> 00:01:17,791
Is she truly injured,

18
00:01:18,375 --> 00:01:19,208
or is she afraid?

19
00:01:19,416 --> 00:01:20,875
Don't tell me

20
00:01:21,916 --> 00:01:22,833
you've all been going easy on her.

21
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:24,833
No.

22
00:01:26,208 --> 00:01:27,333
I accept your challenge, Mr. Lu.

23
00:01:48,750 --> 00:01:49,583
- Bingfan!
- Bingfan!

24
00:01:53,416 --> 00:01:54,208
- Bingfan!
- Bingfan!

25
00:01:54,291 --> 00:01:55,416
So she really is injured.

26
00:01:56,250 --> 00:01:56,833
I'm fine.

27
00:01:57,416 --> 00:01:57,958
Again.

28
00:01:58,208 --> 00:01:58,708
Bingfan.

29
00:01:59,958 --> 00:02:00,666
Stop.

30
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,166
Don't push yourself.

31
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:13,208
I heard Lu Guokai abused his power

32
00:02:13,541 --> 00:02:14,333
and hurt you on purpose.

33
00:02:14,625 --> 00:02:15,833
He just has it out for us.

34
00:02:16,125 --> 00:02:17,291
I'll drag him here right now

35
00:02:17,416 --> 00:02:18,375
and make him apologize to you.

36
00:02:18,375 --> 00:02:18,916
Wait.

37
00:02:21,916 --> 00:02:23,375
Don't go after Lu Guokai.

38
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,125
I lost because I wasn't good enough.

39
00:02:25,416 --> 00:02:26,375
He took advantage of you!

40
00:02:26,375 --> 00:02:27,000
Come on.

41
00:02:27,291 --> 00:02:28,750
Lu Guokai's Wind Blade

42
00:02:29,041 --> 00:02:30,833
is sharp and perfectly controlled.

43
00:02:31,583 --> 00:02:32,875
Even if I weren't injured,

44
00:02:33,416 --> 00:02:34,791
I still wouldn't be his match.

45
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:36,541
If I let you stand up for me

46
00:02:36,958 --> 00:02:37,750
because of this,

47
00:02:38,208 --> 00:02:39,291
I'd be using power to bully him.

48
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:41,208
Then what do you want?

49
00:02:42,458 --> 00:02:44,625
I want to learn to break his Wind Blade.

50
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,625
And I'll defeat him
in the training yard.

51
00:02:53,041 --> 00:02:55,000
Lu Guokai has practiced Wind Blade

52
00:02:55,083 --> 00:02:57,083
for at least 20 years.

53
00:02:57,125 --> 00:03:00,250
Can a few days' training beat it?

54
00:03:00,875 --> 00:03:01,750
My master once said

55
00:03:02,041 --> 00:03:03,166
even the finest martial arts

56
00:03:03,333 --> 00:03:04,958
will reveal a weakness.

57
00:03:05,458 --> 00:03:09,166
Officialdom isn't the martial world.

58
00:03:09,583 --> 00:03:11,625
If you defy your superior like this,

59
00:03:11,875 --> 00:03:13,500
nothing good will come of it.

60
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,000
But he humiliated me in public.

61
00:03:16,166 --> 00:03:18,875
He's your superior and your elder.

62
00:03:19,125 --> 00:03:20,750
What's wrong with yielding a little?

63
00:03:21,416 --> 00:03:22,416
If I yield now,

64
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,208
he'll go even further next time.

65
00:03:24,333 --> 00:03:26,750
Then ask Beiming to speak for you.

66
00:03:27,666 --> 00:03:29,250
If he puts in a word,

67
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:31,333
Lu Guokai will back down.

68
00:03:31,875 --> 00:03:34,041
Why should I ask him to step in?

69
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:36,666
I'll win it back myself.

70
00:03:37,041 --> 00:03:38,958
Why are you so stubborn?

71
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:40,541
So you plan

72
00:03:40,541 --> 00:03:42,666
to fight your superior to the end?

73
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:44,916
I just believe

74
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,041
you get back up where you fell.

75
00:03:48,291 --> 00:03:49,833
If you refuse to bend,

76
00:03:50,625 --> 00:03:51,875
one day,

77
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,916
you'll pay dearly for it.

78
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:17,458
Hua told me

79
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,291
you've gone mad to master Wind Blade.

80
00:04:21,208 --> 00:04:22,166
At the end-of-month assessment,

81
00:04:22,583 --> 00:04:24,791
Lu will use Wind Blade against me.

82
00:04:25,583 --> 00:04:26,583
If I lose again,

83
00:04:26,791 --> 00:04:28,291
even if I'm not expelled
from the Bureau,

84
00:04:28,541 --> 00:04:30,125
I won't get promoted anytime soon.

85
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,250
You want a promotion that badly?

86
00:04:33,666 --> 00:04:34,375
My business

87
00:04:34,791 --> 00:04:35,375
is not something you'd understand.

88
00:04:36,083 --> 00:04:38,208
I want to know. Will you tell me?

89
00:04:39,208 --> 00:04:40,375
Why do you want to hear it?

90
00:04:41,791 --> 00:04:43,000
Because I want to help you.

91
00:04:44,166 --> 00:04:44,666
Fine.

92
00:04:45,458 --> 00:04:46,583
If you truly want to help,

93
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,708
then help me figure out

94
00:04:48,916 --> 00:04:50,916
how to break Lu Guokai's Wind Blade.

95
00:04:54,708 --> 00:04:56,666
Lu's Wind Blade leaves no openings.

96
00:04:56,666 --> 00:04:57,500
It's very hard to break.

97
00:04:57,958 --> 00:04:58,541
Not quite.

98
00:04:59,708 --> 00:05:00,166
Bingfan,

99
00:05:00,541 --> 00:05:01,291
you and Hua,

100
00:05:01,458 --> 00:05:03,250
show me how you fought Lu that day.

101
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,125
I've got it.

102
00:05:33,125 --> 00:05:34,666
Lu Guokai's Wind Blade is powerful,

103
00:05:35,208 --> 00:05:36,875
but he neglects his lower body.

104
00:05:36,875 --> 00:05:37,416
Hua,

105
00:05:37,541 --> 00:05:38,583
can you show her

106
00:05:38,583 --> 00:05:39,875
the Thirty-Six Forms of Ground Boxing?

107
00:05:48,583 --> 00:05:49,125
Got it?

108
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,583
Try it.

109
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:08,750
I understand now.

110
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:15,791
I'll practice some more.

111
00:06:41,541 --> 00:06:42,916
Young... Young Master.

112
00:06:43,083 --> 00:06:44,083
How did you get here?

113
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:47,833
I'm really sorry.

114
00:06:48,541 --> 00:06:50,208
I was too focused on training.

115
00:06:53,708 --> 00:06:54,708
This is

116
00:06:55,791 --> 00:06:57,708
the second time you've hurt me.

117
00:06:57,708 --> 00:06:59,041
Then... what do you want?

118
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:08,208
If you want my forgiveness,

119
00:07:09,333 --> 00:07:10,000
then

120
00:07:10,958 --> 00:07:12,500
give me a massage

121
00:07:13,041 --> 00:07:13,625
and apply medicine.

122
00:07:18,916 --> 00:07:19,416
You arrived.

123
00:07:25,583 --> 00:07:27,166
Why are you taking your clothes off?

124
00:07:27,958 --> 00:07:29,833
Do you apply medicine through clothes?

125
00:07:30,916 --> 00:07:31,541
I...

126
00:07:36,458 --> 00:07:37,416
What are you waiting for?

127
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:41,375
Where... where are you hurt?

128
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,166
Here.

129
00:07:56,875 --> 00:07:58,250
So this is a man's body.

130
00:07:59,291 --> 00:08:00,500
It doesn't look

131
00:08:00,916 --> 00:08:02,458
that different from a woman's.

132
00:08:04,333 --> 00:08:06,750
Why are you making comments on my body?

133
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:39,041
That tickles.

134
00:08:41,333 --> 00:08:42,208
Then do it yourself.

135
00:08:42,666 --> 00:08:43,875
No, you do it.

136
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,583
Young Master Chang.

137
00:08:58,916 --> 00:08:59,708
I...

138
00:09:00,875 --> 00:09:02,125
Just say what you want to say.

139
00:09:02,291 --> 00:09:03,416
This isn't like you.

140
00:09:03,916 --> 00:09:05,500
My master once told me

141
00:09:05,916 --> 00:09:07,750
there's something in a man that's bad.

142
00:09:09,208 --> 00:09:10,583
It can make women pregnant.

143
00:09:10,583 --> 00:09:11,333
What is it?

144
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:12,125
Can I see it?

145
00:09:16,791 --> 00:09:17,791
Are you insane?

146
00:09:22,416 --> 00:09:23,958
Is that something you just ask to see?

147
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:35,000
You can make all kinds of medicine,

148
00:09:35,333 --> 00:09:36,500
and you can cook too.

149
00:09:36,791 --> 00:09:37,916
I've been alone since I was little.

150
00:09:37,916 --> 00:09:39,750
Over time, I learned to do everything.

151
00:09:40,958 --> 00:09:42,041
What about your family?

152
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:43,041
My parents

153
00:09:43,166 --> 00:09:44,916
died when I was very young.

154
00:09:45,291 --> 00:09:46,041
By the way, Hua,

155
00:09:46,666 --> 00:09:50,125
do you know the Ever-Changing Wildcat?

156
00:09:51,875 --> 00:09:53,416
Why bring her up?

157
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,625
I was just asking.

158
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,625
Are you

159
00:09:59,833 --> 00:10:01,083
curious about her?

160
00:10:04,083 --> 00:10:06,416
The only woman in the list's top ten.

161
00:10:06,958 --> 00:10:07,916
Aren't you curious?

162
00:10:08,125 --> 00:10:09,291
Then do you know

163
00:10:10,416 --> 00:10:12,291
why, among the ten most wanted,

164
00:10:12,791 --> 00:10:15,166
she's the only one they want alive?

165
00:10:16,291 --> 00:10:18,625
Because men want to capture her alive,

166
00:10:19,166 --> 00:10:20,041
humiliate her,

167
00:10:21,041 --> 00:10:23,250
and soothe their bruised egos.

168
00:10:24,375 --> 00:10:25,208
And she

169
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,833
has to keep getting stronger,

170
00:10:29,250 --> 00:10:31,333
so they never get what they want.

171
00:10:32,708 --> 00:10:33,750
You understand her well.

172
00:10:35,875 --> 00:10:37,166
I understand women.

173
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:38,375
So,

174
00:10:39,291 --> 00:10:40,625
if I ever meet her,

175
00:10:41,541 --> 00:10:43,166
I'll let her go.

176
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,333
By the way, Hua,

177
00:10:50,791 --> 00:10:52,833
this is the sick-day pill you wanted.

178
00:10:53,208 --> 00:10:54,208
Take one,

179
00:10:54,208 --> 00:10:55,416
and your forehead will heat up.

180
00:10:55,708 --> 00:10:57,333
It'll look just like heatstroke.

181
00:11:02,416 --> 00:11:05,833
Duoyu, your sick-day pill really works.

182
00:11:06,875 --> 00:11:08,958
Help me to your room to rest.

183
00:11:13,333 --> 00:11:14,458
(Firecrackers)
Duoyu.

184
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:17,416
You really are something.

185
00:11:19,458 --> 00:11:21,625
Hua, keep your voice down.

186
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,958
I've never brought anyone here before.

187
00:11:23,958 --> 00:11:25,083
What are you shy about?

188
00:11:30,970 --> 00:11:31,430
(Jinyiwei Handbook)

189
00:11:33,125 --> 00:11:35,166
I just like studying strange things.

190
00:11:36,458 --> 00:11:37,833
The way I see it,

191
00:11:38,875 --> 00:11:42,083
you're no ordinary errand boy.

192
00:11:44,125 --> 00:11:47,125
The assessment is coming up.

193
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:50,041
The Commander is here

194
00:11:50,041 --> 00:11:51,125
to watch your training today.

195
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,500
What would you like to see, my lord?

196
00:11:56,166 --> 00:11:56,666
Short weapons.

197
00:11:56,833 --> 00:11:57,625
Line up!

198
00:12:03,625 --> 00:12:04,791
You three will train today.

199
00:12:06,208 --> 00:12:07,000
Hua Mange.

200
00:12:09,041 --> 00:12:09,875
My lord.

201
00:12:10,291 --> 00:12:11,250
I am

202
00:12:11,833 --> 00:12:13,625
feeling unwell.

203
00:12:14,125 --> 00:12:16,958
My lord, she fainted a few days ago.

204
00:12:16,958 --> 00:12:18,500
It seemed to be heatstroke.

205
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,500
Then next.

206
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:20,291
Cheng Xintian.

207
00:12:20,875 --> 00:12:22,083
My lord.

208
00:12:22,916 --> 00:12:24,125
I'm on my period.

209
00:12:25,958 --> 00:12:26,958
What are you laughing at?

210
00:12:26,958 --> 00:12:28,041
Why are you making a fuss?

211
00:12:28,041 --> 00:12:29,125
You've never had one?

212
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,791
Well...

213
00:12:36,416 --> 00:12:38,583
Shen Bingfan, can you fight?

214
00:12:39,791 --> 00:12:40,583
Yes.

215
00:12:41,458 --> 00:12:43,250
But I would like to challenge Mr. Lu.

216
00:12:43,875 --> 00:12:44,875
What?

217
00:12:53,958 --> 00:12:56,458
Shen Bingfan, who do you think you are?

218
00:12:57,416 --> 00:12:59,125
Do you know what this is called?

219
00:12:59,916 --> 00:13:02,250
Insubordination. Defying your superior.

220
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,125
Do you know the rules or not?

221
00:13:05,333 --> 00:13:06,750
You can't beat him.

222
00:13:07,583 --> 00:13:08,708
I'm willing to try.

223
00:13:09,666 --> 00:13:12,083
Mr. Zhang, she challenged me first.

224
00:13:12,291 --> 00:13:14,583
Don't blame me for bullying my junior.

225
00:13:18,083 --> 00:13:19,958
Prepare extra wound medicine for her.

226
00:13:40,583 --> 00:13:42,541
(Lu Guokai's Wind Blade is powerful,)

227
00:13:42,958 --> 00:13:45,083
(but he overlooks one thing.)

228
00:13:45,291 --> 00:13:46,416
(His lower body.)

229
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:49,375
(Wind Blade
focuses on upper-body attacks.)

230
00:13:49,916 --> 00:13:51,583
(Lu Guokai's footwork is terrible.)

231
00:13:51,875 --> 00:13:53,208
(Once you spot an opening,)

232
00:13:53,208 --> 00:13:54,291
(attack his legs.)

233
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,125
(That should give you a chance to win.)

234
00:14:14,541 --> 00:14:15,625
My lord!

235
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:16,333
Are you all right?

236
00:14:18,166 --> 00:14:19,541
Shen Bingfan!

237
00:14:19,916 --> 00:14:21,750
If I don't kick you out of the Bureau,

238
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,041
I'll eat my hat!

239
00:14:23,041 --> 00:14:24,541
My lord, please compose yourself.

240
00:14:24,541 --> 00:14:25,583
Guokai.

241
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:28,291
You've broadened your mind.

242
00:14:28,291 --> 00:14:29,916
You truly have.

243
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:32,916
I'm deeply moved.

244
00:14:32,916 --> 00:14:33,750
Guokai,

245
00:14:35,333 --> 00:14:36,291
you've opened up.

246
00:14:37,083 --> 00:14:38,416
All the way.

247
00:14:39,333 --> 00:14:41,208
You've truly moved me.

248
00:14:41,208 --> 00:14:43,625
Such consideration for your subordinate.

249
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,750
Did everyone see that?

250
00:14:45,041 --> 00:14:47,333
That is Mr. Lu's magnanimity.

251
00:14:47,541 --> 00:14:48,041
Here.

252
00:14:48,583 --> 00:14:49,041
Thank you.

253
00:14:49,708 --> 00:14:50,375
Have a drink.

254
00:14:51,166 --> 00:14:52,375
What is this taste?

255
00:14:53,583 --> 00:14:55,041
This is a happy occasion.

256
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:56,791
We should all be happy.

257
00:14:57,916 --> 00:14:58,500
Smile.

258
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:00,250
Everyone, smile!

259
00:15:01,166 --> 00:15:01,833
Be happy!

260
00:15:04,041 --> 00:15:05,625
Guokai, take a rest.

261
00:15:08,833 --> 00:15:09,791
Did you see that?

262
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,541
That is true magnanimity.

263
00:15:12,666 --> 00:15:15,291
Mr. Lu held back,

264
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,833
and you clearly learned a great deal.

265
00:15:18,083 --> 00:15:19,500
All right, today

266
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:20,458
we'll

267
00:15:20,458 --> 00:15:21,416
stop here.

268
00:15:22,958 --> 00:15:23,833
Everyone, dismissed.

269
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:25,416
Dismissed. Go on.

270
00:15:25,958 --> 00:15:26,791
Are you feeling better?

271
00:15:26,833 --> 00:15:29,166
Guokai, how generous of spirit.

272
00:15:30,208 --> 00:15:32,250
Help Mr. Lu get back to rest.

273
00:15:33,291 --> 00:15:33,958
Get some rest.

274
00:15:34,125 --> 00:15:34,666
Yes.

275
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:38,958
Add a couple of extra dishes for Mr. Lu.

276
00:15:43,583 --> 00:15:44,166
Move.

277
00:15:49,916 --> 00:15:50,375
Bingfan.

278
00:15:51,625 --> 00:15:52,208
Let's go.

279
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:00,125
You knew when to stop.

280
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:00,875
Good. Very good.

281
00:16:01,208 --> 00:16:02,000
Impressive.

282
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:04,333
Duoyu,

283
00:16:05,416 --> 00:16:07,208
how has Shen Bingfan

284
00:16:09,208 --> 00:16:10,000
been lately?

285
00:16:11,458 --> 00:16:12,041
She's been...

286
00:16:12,041 --> 00:16:12,458
Enough.

287
00:16:13,333 --> 00:16:13,958
Don't say it.

288
00:16:14,708 --> 00:16:15,625
I know.

289
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,750
(Chong'er Pavilion)

290
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:17,208
(Chong'er Pavilion)
Come on.

291
00:16:17,208 --> 00:16:17,833
(Chong'er Pavilion)
Coming.

292
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,291
Come on. A toast to Beiming.

293
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:21,083
Yes, a toast.

294
00:16:21,083 --> 00:16:21,583
Congratulations.

295
00:16:22,166 --> 00:16:22,750
Beiming,

296
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:24,708
you did Miss Shen
a huge favor this time.

297
00:16:24,875 --> 00:16:26,666
That must've earned you major points.

298
00:16:27,208 --> 00:16:28,500
My points were already high.

299
00:16:29,291 --> 00:16:29,875
Of course.

300
00:16:30,375 --> 00:16:31,125
Beiming.

301
00:16:31,125 --> 00:16:34,125
Miss Shen will come see you today.

302
00:16:34,625 --> 00:16:35,416
I think so too.

303
00:16:35,583 --> 00:16:36,416
Why?

304
00:16:36,666 --> 00:16:37,583
To confess her love to you.

305
00:16:38,083 --> 00:16:38,791
Chang Beiming.

306
00:16:40,083 --> 00:16:40,791
Go, go.

307
00:16:40,916 --> 00:16:41,541
Go out.

308
00:16:49,833 --> 00:16:50,500
Chang Beiming.

309
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:52,125
I came to thank you.

310
00:16:52,125 --> 00:16:53,375
Without your help,

311
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,375
I couldn't have beaten Lu's Wind Blade.

312
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:58,041
So you don't hate me anymore?

313
00:16:59,166 --> 00:17:00,625
You are the only man

314
00:17:00,875 --> 00:17:02,000
who can come within three feet of me

315
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,083
without making me uncomfortable.

316
00:17:05,875 --> 00:17:06,875
And you're also

317
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:11,416
one of the male friends
I'd most like to make.

318
00:17:17,958 --> 00:17:18,500
Bingfan,

319
00:17:24,333 --> 00:17:25,625
I like...

320
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:33,875
What happened?

321
00:17:33,875 --> 00:17:34,875
I couldn't help it.

322
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:36,291
What are you doing?

323
00:17:36,666 --> 00:17:37,833
Miss Shen, hi.

324
00:17:38,708 --> 00:17:39,083
We...

325
00:17:39,083 --> 00:17:40,083
We weren't doing anything.

326
00:17:40,083 --> 00:17:40,541
Right.

327
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:41,166
Nothing at all.

328
00:17:42,333 --> 00:17:43,166
They're drunk.

329
00:17:43,458 --> 00:17:44,250
We're not drunk.

330
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:45,333
We were betting on

331
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:47,750
when Beiming would win you over.

332
00:17:48,791 --> 00:17:49,875
What nonsense.

333
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:53,333
Chang Beiming.

334
00:17:53,375 --> 00:17:53,708
No.

335
00:17:54,083 --> 00:17:54,458
You...

336
00:18:00,875 --> 00:18:02,208
Let me explain.

337
00:18:03,375 --> 00:18:04,541
Please, let me explain.

338
00:18:05,708 --> 00:18:06,583
What's there to explain?

339
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:07,583
So you were nice to me

340
00:18:08,166 --> 00:18:09,125
because of a bet.

341
00:18:09,541 --> 00:18:10,041
What...

342
00:18:10,041 --> 00:18:11,791
That's not true.

343
00:18:12,541 --> 00:18:14,125
I knew nothing about their bet.

344
00:18:14,125 --> 00:18:15,333
I really didn't.

345
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:17,958
Then why have you been so nice to me?

346
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:19,458
Because I like you.

347
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:38,270
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

348
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:42,020
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

349
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:45,270
♪My heart drifted lost♪

350
00:18:45,270 --> 00:18:48,680
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

351
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:52,980
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

352
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:56,730
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

353
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:59,520
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

354
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:03,560
♪I've softly let it go♪

355
00:19:03,560 --> 00:19:07,430
♪The vow you made was true♪

356
00:19:07,430 --> 00:19:11,180
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

357
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,390
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

358
00:19:13,390 --> 00:19:17,930
♪And forget at world's end♪

359
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:19,730
♪Embracing memory♪

360
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:22,100
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

361
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:25,980
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

362
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:28,310
♪I wish to let it pass♪

363
00:19:28,310 --> 00:19:33,310
♪And run toward this vast life♪

